{"word":"G2014 - ἐπιφαίνω - epiphaínō - ep-ee-fah'-ee-no - Appear","slug":"G2014","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπιφαίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epiphaínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ee-fah'-ee-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Appear"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>ἐπιφαίνω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Epiphaino</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>ep-ee-fah'-ee-no</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to show to or upon </p> <p class='li520'><b>a.</b> to bring to light </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> to appear, become visible </p> <p class='li520'><b>a.</b> of stars </p> <p class='li260'><b>3.</b> to become clearly known, to show one's self </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5316\">G5316</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 09:07,1 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and <a href=\"#/G5316\">G5316</a>; to <i>shine upon</i> that is <i>become</i> (literally) <i>visible</i> or (figuratively) <b><i>known</i></b>: - appear give light. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1718\">G1718</a>, <a href=\"#/G2015\">G2015</a>, <a href=\"#/G2016\">G2016</a>, <a href=\"#/G5316\">G5316</a>, <a href=\"#/G5318\">G5318</a>, <a href=\"#/G5319\">G5319</a>, <a href=\"#/G5320\">G5320</a>, <a href=\"#/G5321\">G5321</a>, <a href=\"#/G5322\">G5322</a>, <a href=\"#/G5324\">G5324</a>, <a href=\"#/G5325\">G5325</a>, <a href=\"#/G5326\">G5326</a>"}]}